                     <interp inst="t18260406-206-off1111" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18260406-206-cd1112" type="crimeDate">10th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260406-206-off1111 t18260406-206-cd1112"></join>, 1 bag, value 2d.; 5 sovereigns, and 16 shillings, the property of 
                     <persName id="t18260406-206-victim1112" type="victimName">
                        Mary Ann 
                        Ward
                     <interp inst="t18260406-206-victim1112" type="surname" value="Ward"></interp>
